{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2281628, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 438693, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "徐禾 政治经济学概论", "timestamp": 1628997969, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2281637, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 438693, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "资本论有啥背景知识。。。", "timestamp": 1628998091, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2281653, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 438693, "reply_to": 2281628, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 谢谢Alice！", "timestamp": 1628998217, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2281657, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 438693, "reply_to": 2281637, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 呜呜呜dz太菜了......", "timestamp": 1628998242, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2281661, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 438693, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "把马克思拆成三部分。1.哲学，首先读西方哲学史简纲，理清历史唯物主义辩证法在西方哲学体系上的定位。2.政治经济学，首先理清经济学基本几个理论和重要人物，阅读西方经济学在后马克思时代对资本主义的演变和改进。3.科学共产主义。阅读国际共运史，了解列宁先锋队理论，我国共产党早期革命史。了解民主社会主义在欧洲的实践。", "timestamp": 1628998272, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2281674, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 438693, "reply_to": 2281661, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 哇，Carol专业！谢谢Carol！", "timestamp": 1628998397, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2281679, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 438693, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "政治经济学方面，西方对马克思的批判可能比阅读马克思原本更重要，因为200年前的自由资本主义和现在根本不一样。100年前列宁提出帝国资本主义，现今的跨国资本主义和100年前又不一样。", "timestamp": 1628998430, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2281697, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 438693, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "没有马克思主义和国际工人运动，资本家可能早就被一茬又一茬吊路灯了", "timestamp": 1628998569, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2281726, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 438693, "reply_to": 2281697, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 嗯嗯，这就去读！", "timestamp": 1628998857, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 17, "pid": 438693, "reply": 9, "tag": null, "text": "求问大家有没有啥马克思主义入门书推荐呀～\ndz理工科，前些天买了资本论想读一读，结果发现需要的背景知识太多了，想要循序渐进一下～\n（最好是政治经济学方面的书，其他方面的也可以～）", "timestamp": 1628997819, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1628998857, "url": "", "vote": {}}}